Stars in Their Courses - read by Shelby Foote

ISBN 0-679-43466-6
.
Definitive account of the Gettysburg campaign, July 1st, 2nd and 3rd, 1863. 
Unabridged audio recording read by the author. Researched and crafted for 30 years,Foote brilliantly combines Stars in Their Courses - read by Shelby Foote a strategic overview, minute-by-minute tactical narrative and an unerring sense of dramatic detail to create an American Iliad.
